hgaplan

Class hplan

  • java.lang.Object
    • hgaplan.hplan

  • public class hplan
extends java.lang.Object
    Determine the best combination of sexes for the characters in my story"The Hanging Academy". Background: Cardaniel's original story, "Academy Girl," had only women students at the Academy. This suited his secondary theme of gynophagia: everybody needed a certain amount of "girlmeat" in their diet to maintain good health. As a result, all the hangings are of women, and the vast majority of the sex scenes are FF. FF sex doesn't do much for me, so I rewrote it as a furry story with only male students. That makes of of sex scenes MM, which I like better than FF, but not as much as MF. So I'm doing a second rewrite, still furry, but with both male and female students. The purpose of this program is to determine the "best" combination, based on a system that assigns different scores to hangings (M vs. F) and sex scenes (MM, MF, or FF). The main program here finds that combination (I hope) and prints out the results.
